  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Blender_denoiser_VS.gif\" width=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/Blender_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1200&amp;height=540\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/Blender_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"1200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639978\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Blender_denoiser_VS.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"fbe0f265-8137-4845-9d0f-80faeba1427d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/Blender_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1200&amp;height=540 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/Blender_denoiser_VS.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1200&amp;height=540 1x\"></span><p /><p>RenderMan for Blender includes two different denoisers, the RenderMan AI Denoiser from Disney Research (see <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN25/pages/20420808/Denoiser\" data-linked-resource-id=\"20420808\" data-linked-resource-version=\"34\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Denoiser</a>) and <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/optix-denoiser\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nvidia's AI Denoising</a><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\"> solution. </span></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"f3a39527-3d44-48c9-963a-9343a8e2dddd\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Nvidia's AI denoising is not available for macOS.</p></div></div><h2 id=\"DenoiserinBlender-InteractiveRendering\">Interactive Rendering</h2><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">For more information about using the Nvidia denoiser in &quot;it&quot;, refer to the &quot;AI Denoise&quot; section in </span><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN23/pages/19038407/Image+Tool\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19038407\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">Image Tool</span></a><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">.</span></p><p>For interactive renders (viewport renders, IPR to &quot;it&quot;), you can turn on the denoiser by going to the viewport preferences and selecting one of the denoisers under IPR Denoiser. Optix refers to the Nvidia denoiser.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"viewport_options-2.png\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/viewport_options-2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=316&amp;height=326\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/viewport_options-2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"326\" data-width=\"316\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639999\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"viewport_options-2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"0a9097d3-560a-4f26-a908-873df05bb3d7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/viewport_options-2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=316&amp;height=326 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/viewport_options-2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=316&amp;height=326 1x\"></span><p /><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">You should see immediate results with. the Nvidia AI denoiser, like below:</span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/rman_viewport_snapshot_0001_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=556\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/rman_viewport_snapshot_0001_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"791\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640008\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_viewport_snapshot_0001_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"0687b1e2-6c5b-4ba7-9a5a-a72429eda68a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/rman_viewport_snapshot_0001_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1112 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/rman_viewport_snapshot_0001_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725471&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=556 1x\"></span><p /><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">This is the result with the RenderMan AI Denoiser after two passes:</span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/viewport_renderman_denoiser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=540\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/viewport_renderman_denoiser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"769\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640002\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"viewport_renderman_denoiser.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"82f2afe8-2a3e-4a71-9a3d-05740f0ed17f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/viewport_renderman_denoiser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/viewport_renderman_denoiser.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725302&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=540 1x\"></span><p /><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">For the RenderMan AI Denoiser there are some additional controls:</span></p><ul><li><p>Cheap First Pass: if checked, the first denoise pass will use a cheaper (slightly faster but lower quality) heuristic. This can be useful if rendering something that is converging very quickly and you want to prioritize getting a denoised result faster.</p></li><li><p>Min Samples: the minimum number of average samples per bucket before interactive denoising runs for the first time.</p></li><li><p>Interval: the time interval between denoising runs (in seconds).</p></li></ul><p /><p>For preview renders (i.e.: hitting F12 or Render→Render Image), and you're rendering to the the Blender render window, you can select which denoiser you want to use in the Render Properties tab.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preview_denoiser.png\" width=\"409\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=340\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"340\" data-width=\"409\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546996298\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preview_denoiser.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"cca2ed41-8a38-4fbf-9689-22b2a0ab656c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=340 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=340 1x\"></span><p /><p /><p>For the Nvidia AI denoiser, you should immediately see the denoised results in the render window.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preview_render_window.png\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_render_window.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=628\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/preview_render_window.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1112\" data-width=\"1062\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639993\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preview_render_window.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"18fbd482-9431-4ef1-9fe6-2666b574ef15\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_render_window.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1062&amp;height=1112 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_render_window.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=628 1x\"></span><p>For the RenderMan Denoiser, the denoiser will start after the initial render has finished. You should see a message in the render window that denoisnig has started.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"blender_denoising.png\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/blender_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597676987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=632\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/blender_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597676987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1114\" data-width=\"1056\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546897967\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"blender_denoising.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"ef61b059-7332-4b53-afc9-5cfd62962581\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/blender_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597676987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1056&amp;height=1114 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/blender_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597676987&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=632 1x\"></span><p>And here is the final result after denoising (16 sample render).</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"blender_post_denoising.png\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/blender_post_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597772548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=636\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/blender_post_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597772548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1111\" data-width=\"1047\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546930756\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"blender_post_denoising.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"624523f9-544f-43c1-8ee7-466ca096d744\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/blender_post_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597772548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1047&amp;height=1111 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/blender_post_denoising.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754597772548&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=636 1x\"></span><h4 id=\"DenoiserinBlender-Options\">Options</h4><ul><li><p><strong>Use Color Pass</strong>: when unchecked the beauty pass is denoised by coming both the denoised diffuse and denoise specular passes together. This can provide a slightly better result. However, this can cause issues if your scene is using any Display Filters or Sample Filters. If this is the case for you, check this box.</p></li><li><p><strong>Asymmetry</strong>: Controls the asymmetry value, 0 is best quality, higher values encourage the denoiser to avoid overblurring, leading to weaker denoising.</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"DenoiserinBlender-BatchRendering\">Batch Rendering</h2><p>For more general information about batch render in RenderMan For Blender, see <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFB27/pages/544639612/Batch+Rendering+in+Blender\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639612\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Batch Rendering in Blender</a> .</p><p>Note, if you are using Blender Batch, and have the Use Blender Compositor option turned on, then the denoiser setting under the Display section in the render properties tab will be honored.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preview_denoiser.png\" width=\"409\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=340\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"340\" data-width=\"409\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546996298\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preview_denoiser.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"cca2ed41-8a38-4fbf-9689-22b2a0ab656c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=340 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/preview_denoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754596840245&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=340 1x\"></span><p /><p /><p>If you are using RIB batch render style, or have the Use Blender Compositor turned off, you can turn on the denoiser in view layer properties tab. </p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"2437ad45-e9ec-4e57-8a58-23ed05f9e8c2\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>In this batch render workflow only the RenderMan Denoiser can be used. The Nvidia Optix denoiser is not an option</p></div></div><p /><p>You’ll have to switch to RenderMan Displays (for more detailed information on using AOVs in Blender, <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/display/RFB25/AOVs+in+Blender\" rel=\"nofollow\">here is the link!</a>)</p><p /><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Go to the View Layer Properties and click <strong>Switch to RenderMan Displays</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser1.jpg\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=409\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"437\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639990\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"0220930c-f8a1-48b1-8e5a-aa7bd6a49e90\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=437 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725129&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=409 1x\"></span><p /></li><li><p>In the RenderMan Display, select your beauty AOV and turn on <strong>Denoise</strong></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser2.jpg\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=654\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"697\" data-width=\"958\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639987\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"1f97b921-5e8d-4f60-b8e1-fce29396d589\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=958&amp;height=697 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432725128&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=654 1x\"></span><p /></li><li><p>Set any denoiser parameters and you’re all good to go! </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser3.jpg\" width=\"693\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=693&amp;height=434\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"601\" data-width=\"959\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544639984\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544639958\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"7953183f-66f7-412c-9454-50ac7656ba19\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=959&amp;height=601 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544639958/RenderMan_Blender_Denoiser3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432724916&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=693&amp;height=434 1x\"></span><p /></li></ol><p><br/></p>"
